	dprr:hasNoteText "Carried a Lex de sponsu (Gaius 3.121-123, FIRA 2.127; 4.22 and 109, FIRA 2.154 and 175) which preceded a Lex Furia on the same subject (see below, on Furius). See Niccolini, FTP 396f." .
